@"ADVANCED HEAL"
Help for &2Advanced Heal&n

&3Level&n   : 25
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'advanced heal' <self/victim>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Class&n   : Druid, Priest, Paladin, Master

This spell is slightly greater than heal and less powerful than
divine heal! 

See Also: Heal & Divine Heal
#
"ANIMATE DEAD"
Help for &2Animate Dead&n

&3Level&n       : 25
&3Usage&n       : &4cast 'animate dead' corpse&n
&3Accumulative&n: No
&3Class&n       : Magician, Druid, SpellSword, BattleMage & Master

This will animate the dead and allow them to follow you for a 
short period of time.
#
ARMOR
Help for &2Armor&n

&3Level&n       : 1
&3Usage&n       : &4cast 'armor' [self]
&3Accumulative&n: No
&3Duration&n    : 24 Hours
&3Class&n       : Cleric, Druid, Priest, Paladin, Master

The Armor spell will improve your AC by  -15
#
BLESS
Help for &2Bless&n

&3Level&n       : 10
&3Usage&n       : &4cast 'bless' <victim or object>&n
&3Accumulative&n: No
&3Duration&n    : 6 Hours, permanent for objects.
&3Class&n       : Cleric, Druid, Priest, Paladin, Master

Bless on a victim will improve the victims saving throw 
versus spells by 1, and furthermore improve the hitroll 
by 1.

Bless on an item currently has no defined action. It is only possible
to bless non-evil items, and the object blessed may weight no more
than five pounds per level of caster. 

See Also: CURSE
#
BLINDNESS
Help for &2Blindness&n

&3Level&n       : 15
&3Usage&n       : &4cast 'blindness' <victim>&n
&3Accumulative&n: No.
&3Duration&n    : 2 hours
&3Class&n       : Magician, Druid, Priest, Paladin, Master

Blindness will blind a victim failing its saving throw.
A blind person will have -4 penalty to both hitroll and AC.

See Also: AC
#
"BURNING HANDS"
Help for &2Burning Hands&n

&3Level&n   : 5
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'burning hands' <victim>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Save&n    : Versus spell for half damage.
&3Class&n   : Magician, Druid, SpellSword, BattleMage, Master

This spell is more powerful than the chill touch spell.
The Magic User utters this spell and gestures toward the victim.
Tongues of fire lick out from the hands of the Spellcaster, burning 
and searing the target.

See Also: CHILL TOUCH
#
"CALL LIGHTNING"
Help For &2"Call Lightning"&n

&3Level&n   : 15
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'call lightning' <victim>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Save&n    : Versus spell for half damage.
&3Class&n   : Magician, Druid, Spellsword, BattleMage, Master

This spell will use the "forces of nature" to make lightning
strike the victim. It is therefore only possible to call lightning
outside, and it has to be raining (or worse).

The lightning will inflict (level)d8 points of damage, up to a
maximum of 15d8 damage points.

See Also: WEATHER and CONTROL WEATHER
#
CHARM
Help for &2Charm&n

&3Level&n   : 20
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'charm person' <victim>&n
&3Duration&n: (432/Intelligence points of person) hours
&3Save&n    : versus Paralyzation to negate (?)
&3Class&n   : Magician, Druid, SpellSword, BattleMage, Master

This spell will place a person/monster under your control.  Once
charmed, use the command "order" to control them.  It is not possible
to charm anyone who is already under a charm spell, or a higher level
than yourself.  It is also not possible to charm anyone if you are
charmed.  The victim gets a saving throw versus Paralyzation to negate
the spell when cast.

See Also: FOLLOW ORDER 
#
"CHILL TOUCH"
Help For &2"Chill Touch"&n

&3Level&n   : 5
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'chill touch' <victim>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Save&n    : Versus spell for half damage.
&3Class&n   : Magician, Druid, SpellSword, BattleMage, Master

This spell is more powerful than the magic missile spell.

When completed, this spell causes the caster's hands to glow.  The
caster then touches the victim, draining them of their life force.  The
victim gets a saving throw, and if failed they loose 1 point of
Strength.

See Also: MAGIC MISSILE 
#
CLONE
Help For &2Clone&n

&3Level&n       : 65
&3Usage&n       : &4cast 'clone' self&n
&3Accumulation&n: instant
&3class&n       : Cleric, Magician, Druid, SpellSword, Priest,
              BattleMage, Paladin, Master

You can only cast this spell upon yourself and  you can only clone up
to two clones at any one time due to your DNA.

See Also: ORDER SERVE DIE
#
"CLOUD KILL"
Help For &2Cloud Kill&n

&3Level&n : 70
&3Usage&n : &4cast 'cloud; cloud kill'&n
&3Effect&n: Area
&3Class&n : Druid, Spellsword, BattleMage, Master
	
This spell wil summon a powerful cloud of gas that may instantly kill your
victim or cause some serious damage.

#
"COLOR SPRAY"
Help For &2"Color Spray"&n

&3Level&n   : 15
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'color spray' <victim>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Save&n    : Versus spell for half damage.
&3Class&n   : Magician, Druid, SpellSword, BattleMage, Master

This spell is more powerful than the lightning bolt spell.

The Magic User utters this incantation, and a rainbow of clashing colors
springs forth from their hands.

See Also: LIGHTNING BOLT

For help on actual color, see:  ANSI
#
"CONTROL WEATHER"
Help For &2"Control Weather"&n 

&3Level&n       : 30
&3Usage&n       : &4cast 'control weather' ('better' | 'worse')&n
&3Accumulative&n: Yes
&3Class&n       : Cleric, Magician, Druid, SpellSword, Priest
              BattleMage, Paladin, Master

This spell will change the "course" of the current weather.
Exmample:

  > cast 'control wea' worse


See Also: CALL LIGHTNING
#
"CREATE FOOD"
Help For &2"Create Food"&n

&3Level&n   : 1
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'create food'&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Class&n   : Cleric, Thief, Magician, Druid, Priest, Battlemage, 
	   Paladin & Master

This spell instantly creates an edible magic mushroom. The mushroom
will be filling for the next (5+level) hours, up to a maximum of 24 hours.

See Also: CREATE WATER
#
"CREATE WATER"
Help for &2"Create Water"&n 

&3Level&n   : 1
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'create water' <drink container>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Class&n   : Cleric, Thief, Magician, Druid, Priest, Battlemage,
	   Paladin &, Master

Expect disastrous results if cast upon a drink container which contains
another liquid other than water. Empty or water containers will be filled
depending on the level of the caster.

Double amout of water will be created if it is raining (or worse).


See Also: CREATE FOOD

#
"CURE CRITICAL"
Help For &2"Cure Critical"&n

&3Level&n   : 10
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'cure critic' <victim/self>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Class&n   : Cleric, Druid, Priest, Paladin, Master

This spell cures 3d8+3 hitpoints of damage.

#
"CURE LIGHT"
Help For &2"Cure Light"&n

&3Level&n   : 1
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'cure light' <victim/self>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Save&n    : None
&3Class&n   : Cleric, Druid, Priest, Paladin, Master 

This spell cures 1d8 hitpoints of damage.
#
"CURE BLIND"
Help For &2"Cure Blind"&n

&3Level&n   : 5
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'cure blind' <victim/self>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Class&n   : Cleric, Druid, Priest, Paladin, Master

This spell will cure a person blinded by the "blindness" spell, it
can not remove blindness caused by for example cursed items.
 
#
CURSE
Help For &2"Curse"&n

&3Level&n   : 15
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'curse' (victim | object)&n
&3Duration&n: 7 Days, permanent on objects.
&3Save&n    : versus Spell (?)
&3Class&n   : Magician, Druid, SpellSword, BattleMage, Master

Curse cast on a person that fails the saving throw, will reduce the
hitroll by one, and reduce the saving throw versus paralysation by
one. 
#
"DETECT ALIGNMENT"
Help For &2"Detect Alignment"&n

&3Level&n   : 10
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'Detect Alignment'<self/victim>&n
&3Duration&n: 5 hours per level (?)
&3Class&n   : Cleric, Magician, Druid, Priest, Paladin, Master

When cast, this spell enables you to see the Aura of Good/Evil around
monsters and characters.  A Red Aura indicates an Evil soul, whilst a
Blue Aura indicates one who is good.

See Also: ALIGNMENT
 
#
"DETECT INVISIBILITY"
Help for &2Detect Invisibility&n

&3Level&n       : 5
&3Usage&n       : &4cast 'detect invisibility' <self/victim>&n
&3Accumulative&n: Yes
&3Duration&n    : 5 Hours per level
&3Class&n       : Cleric, Magician, Druid, Priest, Battlemage,
	   Paladin & Master

This spell enables you to see invisible items and players.

#
"DETECT MAGIC"
Help For &2"Detect Magic"&n

&3Level&n       : 5
&3Usage&n       : &4cast 'detect magic' <self/victim>&n
&3Accumulative&n: No
&3Duration&n    : 5 hours per level
&3Class&n       : Cleric, Magician, Druid, Priest, Battlemage
	   Paladin & Master

This spell will let you see the magical aura surrounding magical
objects.

#
"DETECT POISON"
Help For &2"Detect Poison"&n

&3Level&n       : 10
&3Usage&n       : &4cast 'detect poison' (victim | food | drink)&n
&3Accumulative&n: No
&3Duration&n    : Instantaneous
&3Class&n       : Cleric, Druid, Priest, Paladin, Master

Cast on food or drinks (drink containers) you will be able to
sense if it is poisoned.

Cast on a person you will be able to see if that person is
poisoned.
 
#
"DISPEL EVIL"
Help For &2"Dispel Evil"&n

&3Level&n   : 25
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'dispel evil' <victim>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Save&n    : Special
&3Class&n   : Cleric, Druid, Priest, Paladin, Master

This spell will only affect evil creatures. An evil person of level
equal or less than caster will suffer 100 damage points.

If the victim is higher level than caster, the spell will inflict
(caster_level)d4 damage points, saving throw versus half damage.

See Also: DISPEL GOOD
#
"DISPEL GOOD"
Help For &2"Dispel Good"&n

&3Level&n   : 25
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'dispel good' <victim>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Save&n    : Special
&3Class&n   : Cleric, Druid, Priest, Paladin, Master

This spell will only affect good creatures.  A good person of level
equal or less than the caster will suffer 100 damage points.

If the vistim is higher level than the caster, the spell will inflict
(caster_level)d4 damage points, saving throw versus half damage.

See Also: DISPEL EVIL
#
"DIVINE HEAL"
Help For &2"Divine Heal"&n

&3Level&n   : 45
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'divine heal' (target)&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Class&n   : Master

Will heal damage done by 300 + caster level.

See Also: Heal & Advanced Heal
#
