The user calls upon their deity for protection. Does -40
to Armor.
#
DRAGON
Help For &2"Dragon"&n

&3Level&n       : 65
&3Usage&n       : &4cast 'dragon' <self>&n
&3Accumulative&n: No
&3Duration&n    : 8 to 10 hours
&3Class&n       : Druid, SpellSword, BattleMage, Master

This will turn you into a dragon that is able to fly and 
depending on your alignment it will add special attributes to 
your person. As you become higher in levels this spell will 
also become more powerful.
#
EARTHQUAKE
Help For &2"Earthquake"&n

&3Level&n   : 15
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'earthquake'&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Class&n   : Magician, Druid, SpellSword, BattleMage, Master

The caster calls upon the great powers of the earth elementals, who cause
the ground itself to rise up and quake underneath their foes.
This spell will damage everybody except the caster by
1d8+level_of_caster hitpoints.

See Also: - 
#
"ENCHANT WEAPON"
Help For &2"Enchant Weapon"&n

&3Level&n       : 40
&3Usage&n       : &4cast 'enchant weapon' <weapon>&n
&3Accumulative&n: No
&3Duration&n    : Permanent
&3Class&n       : Cleric, Magician, Druid, Spellsword, Priest, Battlemage, 
              Paladin, Master

This spell will enchant non-magical (non-modifying) weapons only.
By non-modifying weapons we refer to weapons that might alter any
ability such as for example damage. The only way to know if a weapon
is suitable for enchantment is to fully identify it.

The enchantment will modify the weapon as:

Level    Hit Roll    Damage

 0..17     +1         +1
18..19     +2         +1
20+        +2         +2
#
"ENERGY DRAIN"
Help For &2"Energy Drain"&n

&3Level&n   : 15
&3Usage&n   : &4cast 'energy drain' <victim>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Save&n    : Versus spell for half damage.
&3Class&n   : Magician, Druid, SpellSword, BattleMage, Master

This spell does not give much damage, but victims failing their
saving throws will loose up to 40,000 XP points. You will gain
a quarter of this XP.

Beware! This spell is evil!!
#
FEAR
