&3Usage&n: &4attend <victim>&n
&3Class&n: Cleric, Druid, Priest, Paladin, Master

This is a low healing skill that can be mastered by the healers 
of the game.  There is a limit of 5 uses in 3 tics of play. 
The heal will perform 3*level to a max of 250hps per usage.

See Also: Clot Wounds, First Aid
#
BATTLECRY
Help for &2"Battlecry"&n

&3Level&n   : 30
&3Usage&n   : &4battlecry <victim>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Class&n   : Warrior, Nightblade, Battlemage, Paladin, Master

This skill rolls kick,bearhug,headbutt,piledrive and bash into one, 
as though you did all of these skills seperately. In the way you 
would expect a combo attack to happen. Any of the aforementioned 
skills you have not practice, or do not have the stats for will 
be skipped.

If fighting, not specifying <victim> will hit whoever you're fighting.

See Also: BASH BEARHUG HEADBUTT KICK PILEDRIVE

#
BEARHUG
Help for &2"Bearhug"&n

&3Level&n   : 1
&3Usage&n   : &4bearhug <victim>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Class&n   : Warrior, Nightblade, Battlemage, Paladin, Master

If successful, will do damage to the victim, and 
increase the time before their next attack. 
Damage is based on level and skill effectiveness.

If fighting, not specifying <victim> will hit whoever 
you're fighting.
#
BODYSLAM
Help for &2"Bodyslam"&n 

&3Level&n   : 20
&3Usage&n   : &4bodyslam <victim>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Class&n   : Warrior, Nightblade, Battlemage, Paladin, Master

This attack is used to initiate a fight.  You will 
throw your victim to the ground causing damage depending
on how strong your slam is.
#
DISARM
Help for &2"Disarm"&n

&3Level&n   : 20
&3Usage&n   : &4disarm <victim>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Class&n   : Thief, Warrior, Priest, Nightblade, Battlemage,
          Spellsword, Paladin, Master

This skill once practiced will allow the player to disarm 
an armed component during the attack.  
#
HEADBUTT
Help for &2"Headbutt"&n

&3Level&n   : 30
&3Usage&n   : &4headbutt <victim>&n
&3Duration&n: Instantaneous
&3Class&n   : Thief, Warrior, Priest, Nightblade, Battlemage, Spellsword,
          Paladin, Master

This attack can be used to initiate the fight and then
utilised during the fight to cause more damage.  Beware
over use of this skill can cause permanent damage to
ones self.
