TRIP
Help for &2"Trip"&n 

&3Level&n: 35
&3Usage&n: &4trip <victim>&n
&3Class&n: Thief, Warrior, Priest, Nightblade, Battlemage, 
       Spellsword, Paladin, Master

This skill will trip your intended victim to the ground 
